{"type":null,"faqId":33577,"title":"荣耀7在进行快速充电时为何特别热甚至发烫？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">由于荣耀7快速充电使用的是9V2A充电方式，充电功率会比较大，因此快充时发热量会高于普通充电器充电场景，但仍控制在安全范围之内。市场上所有快速充电都会导致手机发热，荣耀7的发热量相对还算是较小的。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">另外建议用户最好快速充电时不要边充边用，这样会导致发热更加严重，最好是在待机状态下灭屏进行充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">另外在设置-电池中，有一个智能快速充电控制开关，如果用户觉得快速充电时太热，可以选择关闭“智能快速充电”，这样当手机检测当前温度较高时，就会限制充电电流，以降低发热量。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":13,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8297","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748663000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":836,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"快速充电,快充,9V2A,发热,发烫","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}